## Typography

### Font Family
```css
font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
```
**Import**: `@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');`

### Font Weight Scale
- **200-300**: Rarely used, reserved for very large display text
- **400 (Regular)**: Body text, descriptions, secondary labels
- **500 (Medium)**: Subheadings, form labels, secondary buttons
- **600 (Semibold)**: Navigation links, card titles (when not bold)
- **700 (Bold)**: Primary headings, button text, table headers
- **800 (Extrabold/Black)**: Page titles, hero headings

### Type Scale

#### Headings
```css
/* Page Titles (Dashboard, Event Pages) */
.heading-page {
  @apply text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight;
  /* tracking: -0.033em */
}

/* Section Headings (Cards, Panels) */
.heading-section {
  @apply text-lg font-bold;
}

/* Card Titles */
.heading-card {
  @apply text-xl font-bold tracking-tight;
}

/* Subsection Titles */
.heading-subsection {
  @apply text-base font-bold;
}
```

#### Body Text
```css
/* Primary Body */
.body-primary {
  @apply text-base font-normal leading-relaxed;
}

/* Secondary/Muted Body */
.body-secondary {
  @apply text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark;
}

/* Small Text (metadata, timestamps) */
.text-small {
  @apply text-xs;
}
```

#### Labels & UI Elements
```css
/* Form Labels */
.label {
  @apply text-sm font-medium text-text-main dark:text-gray-200 pb-2;
}

/* Button Text */
.button-text {
  @apply text-sm font-bold;
  /* or text-base font-bold for larger buttons */
}

/* Badge/Tag Text */
.badge-text {
  @apply text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide;
}

/* Navigation Links */
.nav-link {
  @apply text-sm font-medium; /* inactive */
  @apply text-sm font-bold; /* active or primary action */
}
```

### Typography Pairing Examples
- **Page Header**: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold` + `text-text-secondary text-lg font-medium` (subheading)
- **Card Header**: `text-lg font-bold` + `text-sm text-text-secondary` (description)
- **Stat Display**: `text-3xl font-bold` (value) + `text-text-secondary font-medium` (label)

