## Accessibility Guidelines

### Color Contrast
- **Body Text**: Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio (WCAG AA)
- **Large Text (18px+)**: Minimum 3:1 contrast ratio
- **Interactive Elements**: Clear focus states with `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50`

### Keyboard Navigation
```html
<!-- Always include focus styles -->
<button class="hover:bg-gray-100 focus:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50">

<!-- Skip link for screen readers -->
<a href="#main-content" class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only">Skip to main content</a>
```

### ARIA & Semantic HTML
- Use semantic HTML (`<nav>`, `<main>`, `<article>`, `<aside>`)
- Add ARIA labels for icon-only buttons: `aria-label="Close dialog"`
- Use `role` attributes when semantic HTML isn't available
- Ensure form inputs have associated `<label>` elements

### Motion & Animation
Consider users with `prefers-reduced-motion`:
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

