## Quality Checklist

Before committing any UI component, verify:

- [ ] **Responsive**: Works on mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1280px+)
- [ ] **Dark Mode**: All states visible and accessible in dark theme
- [ ] **Hover States**: Interactive elements have clear hover/focus indicators
- [ ] **Loading States**: Skeleton loaders or spinners for async content
- [ ] **Empty States**: Helpful messaging when no data exists
- [ ] **Error States**: Clear error messages with recovery actions
- [ ] **Accessibility**: Keyboard navigable, proper ARIA labels, sufficient contrast
- [ ] **Typography**: Consistent with scale (no arbitrary sizes)
- [ ] **Spacing**: Uses spacing scale (no magic numbers)
- [ ] **Colors**: Only uses defined color palette
- [ ] **Icons**: Material Symbols from approved set
- [ ] **Transitions**: Smooth, purposeful animations (200-300ms)

